#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:286
msgid "`ptool.fs.remove(path[, options])` removes a file, symlink, or directory."
msgstr "`ptool.fs.remove(path[, options])` elimina un archivo, enlace simbólico o directorio."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:288
msgid "`path` (string, required): The path to remove."
